<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 18:07:37 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>你需要知道的，第 163 天：面粉在四个月没有援助的情况下抵达加沙地区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-163-flour-reaches-areas-of-gaza-with-no-aid-for-four-months/0000018e-4d89-dc34-a18e-ff8fb3ae0000</link><description>以色列战时内阁将讨论以色列代表团前往卡塔尔的问题 ■ 据报道，面粉卡车已抵达加沙北部地区，这些地区已经四个月没有获得援助了 ■ 德国总理舒尔茨会见总理内塔尼亚胡，表示“我们不能袖手旁观，看着巴勒斯坦人挨饿” ■ 内塔尼亚胡猛烈抨击参议员舒默关于以色列提前选举的呼吁“完全不合适” ■ 战争结束 163 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 18:00:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-163-flour-reaches-areas-of-gaza-with-no-aid-for-four-months/0000018e-4d89-dc34-a18e-ff8fb3ae0000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普表示他会让内塔尼亚胡完成加沙的工作，称“拜登对以色列来说太糟糕了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/trump-on-israel-gaza-war-id-tell-netanyahu-to-finish-it-up-and-do-it-quickly/0000018e-4d59-dca4-ad8e-edffe0df0000</link><description>这位2024年共和党总统候选人告诉福克斯新闻，拜登在看到抗议活动后“抛弃了以色列”，并且“民主党对以色列非常不利”。内塔尼亚胡还在接受福克斯新闻采访时表示，“我感谢特朗普总统对以色列的巨大支持”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 17:44:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/trump-on-israel-gaza-war-id-tell-netanyahu-to-finish-it-up-and-do-it-quickly/0000018e-4d59-dca4-ad8e-edffe0df0000</guid></item><item><title>“我对哈马斯的所作所为感到愤怒，并对以色列政府感到愤怒”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/i-feel-rage-toward-hamas-and-rage-toward-the-israeli-government/0000018e-4d03-d282-a19f-7dd34e340000</link><description>以色列前将军亚伊尔·戈兰（Yair Golan）是反对内塔尼亚胡政府反民主立法的主要声音，现在正在竞选工党领袖，他在国土报-加州大学洛杉矶分校会议上讲述了他认为必须采取哪些措施来稳定该地区以及为什么他这样做对“醒来”的人没有耐心</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 17:34:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/i-feel-rage-toward-hamas-and-rage-toward-the-israeli-government/0000018e-4d03-d282-a19f-7dd34e340000</guid></item><item><title>调查发现，10 月 7 日之后，以色列的团结度急剧上升，对政府的信任度直线下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/after-oct-7-israeli-solidarity-surges-dramatically-trust-in-govt-plummets-survey-finds/0000018e-4bb2-d2fb-a7de-fbf3822e0000</link><description>以色列民主研究所年度民主指数结果显示，在与哈马斯的战争爆发后，人们对军队的信任度很高，对警察的信任度大幅提高，但政治分歧持续存在</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 16:49:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/after-oct-7-israeli-solidarity-surges-dramatically-trust-in-govt-plummets-survey-finds/0000018e-4bb2-d2fb-a7de-fbf3822e0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡猛烈抨击舒默的“完全不恰当”的演讲，拒绝承诺“直到我们赢得战争”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-slams-schumers-inappropriate-speech-says-no-elections-until-war-won/0000018e-4cca-d011-afef-7edefce60000</link><description>总理在美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 露面时谴责参议院多数党领袖要求下台的“完全不恰当”的呼吁，并断然否认以色列希望举行选举的说法。前议长佩洛西称赞舒默的讲话是“对以色列的爱之举”</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 15:11:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-slams-schumers-inappropriate-speech-says-no-elections-until-war-won/0000018e-4cca-d011-afef-7edefce60000</guid></item><item><title>“以色列定居者现在可以为所欲为。他们想赶走住在那里的人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-settlers-can-now-do-whatever-they-please-like-driving-off-those-who-live-there/0000018e-135d-d32b-ab8f-bb7df1270000</link><description>埃雷拉·杜纳耶夫斯基 (Erella Dunayevsky) 几十年来一直是约旦河西岸的以色列活动人士，她对解决冲突已经失去了希望。她的新书详细描述了南希伯伦山无数的骚扰和暴力事件</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 14:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israeli-settlers-can-now-do-whatever-they-please-like-driving-off-those-who-live-there/0000018e-135d-d32b-ab8f-bb7df1270000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人设想在加沙和以色列之间修建一条运河</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-who-envisioned-a-canal-between-gaza-and-israel/0000018e-2e2c-d3eb-abbe-7eec0b2f0000</link><description>随着他的视频作品“加沙运河”重新获得关注，塔米尔·扎多克谈到了创作与宣传之间的讽刺性徘徊，并对围绕他的侄子、导演尤瓦尔·亚伯拉罕的风暴做出了反应</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 12:04:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-03-17/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-israeli-who-envisioned-a-canal-between-gaza-and-israel/0000018e-2e2c-d3eb-abbe-7eec0b2f0000</guid></item><item><title>由于没有结束与巴勒斯坦人冲突的愿景，以色列证明它没有从 10 月 7 日事件中吸取任何教训</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/with-no-vision-to-end-conflict-with-hamas-israel-proves-it-learned-nothing-from-oct-7/0000018e-4bfc-d2fb-a7de-fbff810f0000</link><description>以色列为阻止巴勒斯坦建国而采取的拖延和临时政策没有改变，但双方的破坏和痛苦的规模却只增不减</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 11:35:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/with-no-vision-to-end-conflict-with-hamas-israel-proves-it-learned-nothing-from-oct-7/0000018e-4bfc-d2fb-a7de-fbff810f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯达成协议的机会取决于内塔尼亚胡给予卡塔尔代表团多少回旋余地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegations-room-for-maneuver-key-to-clinching-hostage-deal/0000018e-490c-d1ed-a7ef-5d1fdd140000</link><description>哈马斯在人质谈判中对调解人的答复为达成潜在协议打开了大门，但内塔尼亚胡总理坚持取得“全面胜利”，这表明以色列不太可能表现出太大的灵活性</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 04:07:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegations-room-for-maneuver-key-to-clinching-hostage-deal/0000018e-490c-d1ed-a7ef-5d1fdd140000</guid></item><item><title>德国的肖尔茨与内塔尼亚胡一起谴责加沙的饥饿，敦促以色列和哈马斯通过人质协议实现“长期”停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article-live/israeli-officials-hamas-reply-in-gaza-hostage-talks-indicates-achievements/0000018e-4a77-d7e6-af9e-fffff8be0005</link><description>巴勒斯坦消息人士称，哈马斯副军事首长在以色列袭击中受伤，《卫报》报道称，以色列官员怀疑在袭击中丧生 ■ 领导人质交易谈判的摩萨德负责人预计将于周一前往多哈 ■ 总理办公室称战争内阁和政治安全内阁将讨论谈判小组启程前往卡塔尔进行人质交易谈判 ■ 德国总理将在特拉维夫会见内塔尼亚胡</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 04:03:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article-live/israeli-officials-hamas-reply-in-gaza-hostage-talks-indicates-achievements/0000018e-4a77-d7e6-af9e-fffff8be0005</guid></item><item><title>以色列扩大西岸自然保护区面积，将非法定居点纳入其中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-expands-area-of-west-bank-nature-reserve-to-include-illegal-settlement-outpost/0000018e-495e-d75f-abff-d9ffd2ef0000</link><description>以色列民政管理局的命令旨在确保保护区内不会进行非法建筑，但该机构并未执行其之前针对前哨基地建设的命令，多年来，该前哨基地的活动不断扩大</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 23:01:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-17/ty-article/.premium/israel-expands-area-of-west-bank-nature-reserve-to-include-illegal-settlement-outpost/0000018e-495e-d75f-abff-d9ffd2ef0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯对加沙协议的最新回应：内塔尼亚胡斥为“荒谬”，官员称该协议对以色列有重大进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/latest-hamas-response-for-gaza-deal-proposal-includes-gains-for-israel-officials-say/0000018e-48d3-d2fb-a7de-f9f32f550000</link><description>哈马斯宣布这一消息后，释放加沙以色列人质谈判的主要争论点是要求允许加沙北部居民返回家园，因为担心该组织重新控制该地区</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 20:53:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/latest-hamas-response-for-gaza-deal-proposal-includes-gains-for-israel-officials-say/0000018e-48d3-d2fb-a7de-f9f32f550000</guid></item><item><title>法国和德国大使与数千名以色列人一起集会，要求人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-joined-by-french-and-german-envoys-rally-to-demand-hostage-deal/0000018e-4850-d2fb-a7de-f9f395610000</link><description>数百人参加了人质家属的自发游行，封锁了特拉维夫的一条主要街道。人质被哈马斯劫持五个月后，其家人和欧洲高级大使恳求政府达成协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 19:50:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/thousands-of-israelis-joined-by-french-and-german-envoys-rally-to-demand-hostage-deal/0000018e-4850-d2fb-a7de-f9f395610000</guid></item><item><title>您需要了解的第 162 天：急救船抵达加沙，联合国儿童基金会警告存在严重营养不良</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-162-first-aid-ship-reaches-gaza/0000018e-4867-d75f-abff-d8ff81330000</link><description>急救船向加沙运送220吨食品 ■ 德国首次向加沙地带空投 ■ 联合国儿童基金会：加沙北部每三个两岁以下儿童中就有一个严重营养不良 ■ 以色列摩萨德负责人将于周一在多哈恢复加沙停火谈判■ 以色列国防军击毙向希伯伦犹太社区开枪的巴勒斯坦枪手 ■ 战争开始 162 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 18:20:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-162-first-aid-ship-reaches-gaza/0000018e-4867-d75f-abff-d8ff81330000</guid></item><item><title>以色列各地数千人抗议内塔尼亚胡政府，要求甘茨放弃战时联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/israelis-protest-netanyahu-govt-across-the-country-demand-gantz-ditch-wartime-coalition/0000018e-47a4-d7ea-a5de-7fb54b7f0000</link><description>抗议者聚集在以色列最大的城市以及内塔尼亚胡的私人和官邸外，要求提前举行选举，一些人还呼吁中间派战时内阁成员本尼·甘茨及其政党退出政府并“停止向总理伸出援手”</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 18:06:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/israelis-protest-netanyahu-govt-across-the-country-demand-gantz-ditch-wartime-coalition/0000018e-47a4-d7ea-a5de-7fb54b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>“不想给本格维尔借口”：斋月第一个星期五的祈祷在耶路撒冷悄然过去</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/didnt-want-to-give-ben-gvir-excuses-first-friday-prayers-of-ramadan-quiet-in-jerusalem/0000018e-47f3-d2fb-a7de-f7f3c9370000</link><description>数万名穆斯林信徒在阿克萨清真寺参加祈祷，这是自加沙战争开始以来耶路撒冷最平静的星期五 ■ 对于所有认为这座城市不仅仅是冲突区的人来说，这是一场胜利</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 16:34:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/didnt-want-to-give-ben-gvir-excuses-first-friday-prayers-of-ramadan-quiet-in-jerusalem/0000018e-47f3-d2fb-a7de-f7f3c9370000</guid></item><item><title>被指控加入哈马斯的贝都因以色列人在监狱牢房中被发现失去知觉后死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-israeli-accused-of-joining-hamas-dies-after-being-found-unconscious-in-prison-cell/0000018e-47d4-d75f-abff-dfff8b620000</link><description>朱马·阿布·加尼玛 (Juma Abu Ghanima) 于 2016 年越过边境进入加沙，并于去年 12 月试图返回以色列。根据他的起诉书，他曾与哈马斯的努赫巴部队一起训练，并提供了有关以色列军事基地的信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 15:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article/.premium/bedouin-israeli-accused-of-joining-hamas-dies-after-being-found-unconscious-in-prison-cell/0000018e-47d4-d75f-abff-dfff8b620000</guid></item><item><title>战时内阁将讨论卡塔尔加沙谈判条款；报道：以色列袭击叙利亚南部军事基地</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article-live/netanyahu-approves-plans-for-rafah-operation-sends-delegation-to-qatar/0000018e-44b2-d7ea-a5de-7cb724320000</link><description>以色列各地举行人质释放协议示威、提前选举 ■ 以色列官员表示，哈马斯对加沙人质协议提案的最新回应取得了成果 ■ 总理办公室表示，战时内阁将讨论谈判小组前往卡塔尔进行人质协议谈判 ■ 美国中央司令部航空-与约旦联合行动向加沙北部空投援助</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 00:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-16/ty-article-live/netanyahu-approves-plans-for-rafah-operation-sends-delegation-to-qatar/0000018e-44b2-d7ea-a5de-7cb724320000</guid></item><item><title>一名巴勒斯坦男孩在父亲面前被以色列军队开枪射杀，死在哥哥怀里</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-03-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/he-was-shot-by-israeli-troops-in-front-of-his-father-and-died-in-his-brothers-arms/0000018e-4466-d1ed-a7ef-557737090000</link><description>当一位父亲和他的两个小儿子在村里办完事后开车回家时，以色列士兵向他们的皮卡车开枪，打死了 10 岁的孩子。饱受创伤的 7 岁孩子为弟弟的死自责</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Mar 2024 00:16:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-03-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/he-was-shot-by-israeli-troops-in-front-of-his-father-and-died-in-his-brothers-arms/0000018e-4466-d1ed-a7ef-557737090000</guid></item><item><title>报复后自杀的破坏性愿望植根于以色列的精神</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-destructive-wish-for-revenge-followed-by-suicide-is-rooted-in-the-israeli-ethos/0000018e-42e8-de41-adef-d7ed95dc0000</link><description>民族宗教和世俗团体都怀有比单纯复仇的愿望更深刻、更古老的理想</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 23:12:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-destructive-wish-for-revenge-followed-by-suicide-is-rooted-in-the-israeli-ethos/0000018e-42e8-de41-adef-d7ed95dc0000</guid></item></channel></rss>